00:21:03.680 --> 00:21:04.830
Ich müsste Jin anrufen.

00:21:04.830 --> 00:21:05.720
"Ältere Schwester".

00:21:06.350 --> 00:21:07.190
Ungeschickte Hierarchie.

00:21:08.310 --> 00:21:09.240
